corpus: Google LLC is an American multinational technology company focusing on artificial intelligence, search engines, online advertising, and cloud computing. Google was founded on September 4, 1998 by Larry Page and Sergey Brin.

Apple Inc. is an American multinational technology company specializing in consumer electronics and software. Apple is the largest technology company by revenue and the most valuable company in the world.
